{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3116046b80","title":"给陈瑾昆的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"60f82d7e7f","index":0,"year":1947,"month":11,"day":18,"articleId":"3116046b80"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"00f6f24a78","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":4,"text":"陈瑾昆，当时任中共中央法律委员会委员。"},{"id":"0e7eb4cdaa","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80","index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":173,"text":"王，指王明，即陈绍禹（一九○四——一九七四），安徽金寨人，当时任中共中央法律委员会主任。谢，指谢觉哉（一八八四——一九七一），湖南宁乡人，当时是中共中央法律委员会负责人之一。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8ab3755c6c","type":"title","text":"给陈瑾昆的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80"},{"id":"00f6f24a78","type":"appellation","text":"瑾昆同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80"},{"id":"0e7eb4cdaa","type":"paragraph","text":"十月八日来示敬悉。国内外大势观察正确，不会有第二个方向，进度亦快，不会稽延不决，诚如尊论。惟我们宁可作从长打算，估计到一切可能的困难，以自力更生精神，准备付以较长时间，似属有益。兄及诸同志对于宪草惨淡经营，不胜佩慰。惟发表时机尚未成熟，内容亦宜从长斟酌，以工农民主专政为基本原则（即拙著《新民主主义论》及《论联合政府》中所指之基本原则），详由王谢二同志面达。弟身体有时略有毛病，大体尚好，勿以为念。天寒尚祈珍摄。敬祝安好！并问陈夫人及诸小弟妹好！","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80"},{"id":"2fb11f5f17","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80"},{"id":"65644706fb","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四七年十一月十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80"},{"id":"c6ffc17c53","type":"paragraph","text":"江青附笔祝全家安好！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80"},{"id":"51846b8376","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80"},{"id":"7b44d06d35","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80"}],"page":{"id":"9ae8eecf05","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"3116046b80","start":334,"end":334}}}},"__N_SSG":true}